{"tid":1000862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"酒池肉林再進化！杭州酒店推九宮格火鍋溫泉　浸辣椒香蕉歎豬肉串","createTime":"2019-01-29T16:58:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T16:32:25.000Z","uid":66271,"like":9,"dislike":301,"uniUserReply":117,"replies":[{"pid":"eabf571ef440a0150afbee810696ab52fccf5494","tid":1000862,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T16:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2380462/org/1dd2eb42a060f12d8e4d8c5e735e852d.jpg/sxl53ThLaxHdpO5rowUv_4o7ldkei6IaPsUQ8T7FEPE?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2380462%2Forg%2F1dd2eb42a060f12d8e4d8c5e735e852d.jpg%2Fsxl53ThLaxHdpO5rowUv_4o7ldkei6IaPsUQ8T7FEPE%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=f5ae291a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n也許半鍋辣椒、半鍋蔬菜的「鴛鴦火鍋溫泉」未夠震撼，為迎豬年，杭州有溫泉酒店再推進化版「巨型九宮格火鍋溫泉」，九宮格各小池中分別放滿辣椒、香蕉、蘋果、粟米等蔬果，讓顧客在「火鍋」中浸着各種配料，同時可以大啖吃菜和豬肉串。不過有內地網民認為這個變奏版「特色鍋」低俗，批評酒店浪費食物，估計顧客泡完溫泉後，一整鍋食材也不能要了，有人更不禁反諷「別說那些用完的水果再撈出來賣」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2380466/org/2d454392579b888abc5c19974676673a.jpg/CPyac6tWa0xxtS9urOG9W1OHFhf1tVlltkQXqbZEF6k?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2380466%2Forg%2F2d454392579b888abc5c19974676673a.jpg%2FCPyac6tWa0xxtS9urOG9W1OHFhf1tVlltkQXqbZEF6k%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=c23b6ec3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為迎接豬年，酒店再推進化版火鍋溫泉，今次以九宮格火鍋為主題，酒店在每格放滿辣椒、生菜、番茄、金桔、青棗、蘋果、粟米、香蕉、菇菌等9種蔬果，池中央架着3大串豬肉串，讓各自泡浸在火鍋格的顧客，張開口便可吃到豬肉串。酒店更表示要向屬豬的顧客送上祝福，在正月初一至十五期間，全國屬豬的客人只要提前一天打電話預約，憑身份證可免費泡浸溫泉及到爛蘋果樂園遊玩。<br />\n<br />\n如早前推出的「鴛鴦溫泉火鍋」一樣，網民看到這款九宮格火鍋溫泉，都不禁質疑衛生問題，感覺這樣吃火鍋很髒，「那些蔬菜還能吃嗎？」，更多人批評酒店此舉浪費食物，「真的好低俗，糧食用來吃好不好嗎？」、「泡完的食物怎麼處理？」，亦有人擔心泡浸完的水果會被撈出來再賣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2380487/org/10cfe4b42201ba9786cf9c752aba8ed1.jpg/fC2EY-Yvo0u7S-RvCdSIjlyO8O6qGzxMmrdwk5q3cJM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2380487%2Forg%2F10cfe4b42201ba9786cf9c752aba8ed1.jpg%2FfC2EY-Yvo0u7S-RvCdSIjlyO8O6qGzxMmrdwk5q3cJM&h=4412d8b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2380482/org/0d2787eb3980a29c1aaa72f56ff6ad7e.jpg/zni5Ad6Y-RMiJOtTSSIdM2NCUN-4kfqiZdzwuGXc8Lg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2380482%2Forg%2F0d2787eb3980a29c1aaa72f56ff6ad7e.jpg%2Fzni5Ad6Y-RMiJOtTSSIdM2NCUN-4kfqiZdzwuGXc8Lg&h=bbad2aa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2380484/org/4dd920dbe99a70cd4c368c98d7581830.jpg/8OD0gjeytRUty0OYXXqtfQ3QLk39H7Q_urmu4rq5ruI\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2380484%2Forg%2F4dd920dbe99a70cd4c368c98d7581830.jpg%2F8OD0gjeytRUty0OYXXqtfQ3QLk39H7Q_urmu4rq5ruI&h=e71a3ded&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2380488/org/8599fa0581cf9338275cebfb68d98d36.jpg/JLim6o761QC02FrQrbt7ywml84iK-Bj8J5TW-CeU1vg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2380488%2Forg%2F8599fa0581cf9338275cebfb68d98d36.jpg%2FJLim6o761QC02FrQrbt7ywml84iK-Bj8J5TW-CeU1vg&h=b79c64ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8b69ce0e02a9b63e5793d36bcd3dac8b36775f9","tid":1000862,"uid":13008,"like":1,"dislike":53,"score":-52,"quote":{"pid":"eabf571ef440a0150afbee810696ab52fccf5494","tid":1000862,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T16:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2380462/org/1dd2eb42a060f12d8e4d8c5e735e852d.jpg/sxl53ThLaxHdpO5rowUv_4o7ldkei6IaPsUQ8T7FEPE?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2380462%2Forg%2F1dd2eb42a060f12d8e4d8c5e735e852d.jpg%2Fsxl53ThLaxHdpO5rowUv_4o7ldkei6IaPsUQ8T7FEPE%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=f5ae291a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n也許半鍋辣椒、半鍋蔬菜的「鴛鴦火鍋溫泉」未夠震撼，為迎豬年，杭州有溫泉酒店再推進化版「巨型九宮格火鍋溫泉」，九宮格各小池中分別放滿辣椒、香蕉、蘋果、粟米等蔬果，讓顧客在「火鍋」中浸着各種配料，同時可以大啖吃菜和豬肉串。不過有內地網民認為這個變奏版「特色鍋」低俗，批評酒店浪費食物，估計顧客泡完溫泉後，一整鍋食材也不能要了，有人更不禁反諷「別說那些用完的水果再撈出來賣」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2380466/org/2d454392579b888abc5c19974676673a.jpg/CPyac6tWa0xxtS9urOG9W1OHFhf1tVlltkQXqbZEF6k?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2380466%2Forg%2F2d454392579b888abc5c19974676673a.jpg%2FCPyac6tWa0xxtS9urOG9W1OHFhf1tVlltkQXqbZEF6k%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=c23b6ec3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為迎接豬年，酒店再推進化版火鍋溫泉，今次以九宮格火鍋為主題，酒店在每格放滿辣椒、生菜、番茄、金桔、青棗、蘋果、粟米、香蕉、菇菌等9種蔬果，池中央架着3大串豬肉串，讓各自泡浸在火鍋格的顧客，張開口便可吃到豬肉串。酒店更表示要向屬豬的顧客送上祝福，在正月初一至十五期間，全國屬豬的客人只要提前一天打電話預約，憑身份證可免費泡浸溫泉及到爛蘋果樂園遊玩。<br />\n<br />\n如早前推出的「鴛鴦溫泉火鍋」一樣，網民看到這款九宮格火鍋溫泉，都不禁質疑衛生問題，感覺這樣吃火鍋很髒，「那些蔬菜還能吃嗎？」，更多人批評酒店此舉浪費食物，「真的好低俗，糧食用來吃好不好嗎？」、「泡完的食物怎麼處理？」，亦有人擔心泡浸完的水果會被撈出來再賣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2380487/org/10cfe4b42201ba9786cf9c752aba8ed1.jpg/fC2EY-Yvo0u7S-RvCdSIjlyO8O6qGzxMmrdwk5q3cJM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2380487%2Forg%2F10cfe4b42201ba9786cf9c752aba8ed1.jpg%2FfC2EY-Yvo0u7S-RvCdSIjlyO8O6qGzxMmrdwk5q3cJM&h=4412d8b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2380482/org/0d2787eb3980a29c1aaa72f56ff6ad7e.jpg/zni5Ad6Y-RMiJOtTSSIdM2NCUN-4kfqiZdzwuGXc8Lg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2380482%2Forg%2F0d2787eb3980a29c1aaa72f56ff6ad7e.jpg%2Fzni5Ad6Y-RMiJOtTSSIdM2NCUN-4kfqiZdzwuGXc8Lg&h=bbad2aa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2380484/org/4dd920dbe99a70cd4c368c98d7581830.jpg/8OD0gjeytRUty0OYXXqtfQ3QLk39H7Q_urmu4rq5ruI\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2380484%2Forg%2F4dd920dbe99a70cd4c368c98d7581830.jpg%2F8OD0gjeytRUty0OYXXqtfQ3QLk39H7Q_urmu4rq5ruI&h=e7